snippet.title: Amber Perfumes // 14 Amber Fragrances That I Adore
snippet.description:
Hey Everyone!! Today I have 14 Amber fragrances from my collection to share with you. I think I have a bit of something for everyone here. I hope you enjoy!!

Fragrances Mentioned:
Madonna Truth or Dare Naked
Halston Woman Amber
Carner Barcelona Ambar Del Sur
Aerin Amber Musk
Aerin Amber Musk D'or
Laura Mercier Ambre Vanille
Michael Kors Sexy Amber
J. Del Pozo Ambar
Armani Si Le Parfum
Laura Mercier Amber Passion
John Paul Gaultier Gaultier 2
Histoires de Parfums Ambre 114
